      "content": "look i'm not asking you to be my doctor i'm just asking for the info. i already know the standard dose is like 400 or 800 but i've read online that people sometimes take much more for severe inflammation. if i took like 1200mg or even 2000mg of ibuprofen just this once to get through the night, is that actually going to kill me or is it just a precaution? it feels like a lot of people do it when they have real issues.",
